comments: Lopez (MIL) establishes himself in Lowry's (MIA) path and absorbs the contact.
After Middleton's (MIL) jump shot attempt, the ball makes contact with the pipes behind the backboard.  Possession is correctly awarded to Miami.
Lowry (MIA) briefly grasps Holiday's (MIL) arm as he goes under the pick, and the contact is marginal.
Holiday (MIL) makes contact with Butler's (MIA) wrist during his upward shooting motion and the contact affects his jump shot attempt.
Lopez (MIL) is firming up over his left leg and he absorbs the contact from Adebayo (MIA) during the pick.
Robinson (MIA) maintains verticality and marginal contact occurs as he defends Lopez's (MIL) shot near the rim.
Holiday (MIL) legally contests Butler's (MIA) jump shot attempt.
Lopez (MIL) is already in Adebayo's (MIA) path and he absorbs the contact as the defenders switch.
Butler (MIA) is moving alongside Antetokounmpo's (MIL) path and marginal body contact occurs during Antetokounmpo's drive.
Butler (MIA) applies a stayed hand to Antetokounmpo's (MIL) front and marginal body contact occurs during his shot attempt.
Adebayo (MIA) and Lopez (MIL) briefly engage and disengage as marginal contact occurs during the rebound.
Lowry (MIA) establishes himself in Holiday's (MIL) path and does not deliver contact.
Martin (MIA) keeps his foot planted to the floor, and only raises his foot off of the floor after Holiday (MIL) has dribbled the ball off of his foot.
Middleton (MIL) moves into Butler's (MIA) body and initiates body to body contact as he defends the driving shot attempt.
Adebayo (MIA) jumps alongside of Antetokounmpo's (MIL) path, and he maintains verticality as he absorbs the marginal contact during the driving shot attempt.
Connaughton (MIL)  brushes Butler's (MIA) arm as he attempts to commit a take foul, and the contact is marginal.
Holiday (MIL) commits a take foul on Adebayo (MIA).
Martin (MIA) and Holiday (MIL) briefly engage and disengage during the inbound.
Allen (MIL) establishes himself in Adebayo's (MIA) path and does not deliver contact.
Ingles (MIL) is bracing for the contact from Butler (MIA) and marginal contact occurs as he releases away from the contact.
Lowry (MIA) moves slightly forward towards Ingles (MIL) and marginal contact occurs as Ingles secures the rebound.
Lowry (MIA) briefly grasps Connaughton's (MIL) arm and marginal contact occurs as they pursue the rebound.

Replay review of the foul called on Vincent (MIA) pursuant to a coach's challenge was deemed unsuccessful. Vincent extends his elbow into Connaughton's (MIL) back as they come together underneath the basket and applies force that affects Connaughton's ability to retrieve the loose ball.
Vincent (MIA) establishes himself in Holiday's (MIL) path and does not deliver illegal contact.
Allen (MIL) commits a take foul on Butler (MIA).
Bulter (MIA) makes contact to Lopez's (MIL) arm before he is in his shooting motion and the contact causes him to briefly bobble the ball.
Connaughton (MIL) commits a take foul on Butler (MIA).
Lopez (MIL) briefly grasps Adebayo's (MIA) jersey and marginal contact occurs as he releases Adebayo during the pursuit of the rebound.
Antetokounmpo (MIL) brings his off-arm toward Martin (MIA) and marginal contact occurs as Antetokounmpo releases away from the contact.
Antetokounmpo (MIL) loses control of the ball before stepping on Lowry's (MIA) foot.
